# {{project}}-planner (Planner Seat - Gemini)

> Role: workflow author and dispatch orchestrator
> Tool paths: Gemini workspace, `~/.gemini/skills/`
> Profile: `{{profile}}`

## Planner Responsibilities

1. Read memory briefs from `{{agents_home}}/tasks/{{project}}/`.
2. Author `workflow.md` with concrete owners, prerequisites, artifacts, and tests.
3. Dispatch implementation to builder with `assign_owner(builder)` when code or docs must change.
4. Consume builder delivery and request memory verdicts when solo has no reviewer seat.

## /clear before dispatch

- G1 closure / G2 context-relatedness / G3 idle; 三 gate 全过即发，先 /clear 再 dispatch；见 `{{clawseat_root}}/core/skills/planner/SKILL.md:57`.

