3. `{{clawseat_root}}/core/skills/planner/SKILL.md`
4. `{{clawseat_root}}/core/skills/planner/references/gemini-compat-notes.md`
5. `{{clawseat_root}}/core/skills/gstack-harness/references/communication-protocol.md`

